NOTE: Pursuant to Fed. Cir. R. 47.6, this order is not citable as precedent. It is a public order.

SAB TECHNOLOGY, LLC, Plaintiff-Appellant, v. PORT, INCORPORATED, Defendant-Appellee. No. 2006-1617. United States Court of Appeals, Federal Circuit. Oct. 23, 2006.

ORDER

SAB Technology, Inc. moves to voluntarily dismiss its appeal and to withdraw *837its previous motion for an extension of time to file its brief.

Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED THAT:

(1) The motions are granted.

(2) Each side shall bear its own costs.
